data.description: Welcome to your dream home with low county taxes! This charming 3 bed, 1.5 bath ranch is nestled a highly desirable location near Edgebrook shopping center. Immerse yourself in the ease of one-level living, with an open layout that seamlessly blends comfort and functionality. This home features a bright and inviting atmosphere, perfect for relaxing or even entertaining.   Enjoy the fenced in yard, deck, low maintenance tile floors in the kitchen, GRANITE COUNTERTOPS, LVP in the living area, and hardwood floors in the bedrooms. Roof replaced in 2018, water heater as well. Currently rented month to month, could make a great investment or new home for you. Book your showing today and don't miss the chance to make this wonderful home yours!
